Global Two-phase Motor Market Insights
Two-phase Motor Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Two-phase Motor Market Overview
The global two-phase motor market is experiencing significant growth, driven by advancements in motor technology and increasing demand for energy-efficient solutions across various industries. In 2023, the market was valued at approximately USD 1.2 billion and is projected to reach USD 2.8 billion by 2032, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 8.5% during the forecast period. This growth is attributed to the rising adoption of two-phase motors in automotive, industrial machinery, and consumer electronics sectors, where their high efficiency and reliability are highly valued.

